data.description: SELLER OFFERING $10,000 BUYER CREDIT AT CLOSING TOWARD CARPET AND PAINT. Nice open living home with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. 20' coffered ceiling in living room, arched openings for dining room and arched opened loft flex space. Kitchen with granite, island, pantry, double ovens and new refrigerator, dishwasher and microwave. Master suite includes vaulted ceiling in bedroom and bath, sitting area and two walk-in closets. Bedrooms 3 and 4 have vaulted ceiling. Privacy fenced backyard with drive-in gate, covered back porch, a patio, playhouse and shed. One bedroom, full bath and laundry room downstairs. Wood burning fireplace behind TV in living room. No HOA! Convenient to I-24 and Ft. Campbell.
